            <div class="title">
                Court-Martial (Newspaper Comments)
            </div>

            <div class="right-arrow">
                    <a href="/Commons/1951-02-01/debates/b7ec872b-0805-45c7-b5d4-d4cf7d5e89f5/BusinessOfTheHouse" class="next" title="Go to the next debate">
